{"word":"ἀποτίθημι","slug":"ἀποτίθημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀποτίϑημι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, τίϑημι</el>] central idea. ‘put off’; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a><b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> <i>put away, lay aside, rid oneself of</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of things: garments <b><a href='B:510 7:58'>Ac 7:58</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> bad deeds or disposition <b><a href='B:520 13:12'>Ro 13:12</a>; <a href='B:560 4:22'>Eph 4:22</a>, <a href='B:560 4:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:580 3:8'>Col 3:8</a>; <a href='B:650 12:1'>Hb 12:1</a>; <a href='B:660 1:21'>Js 1:21</a>; <a href='B:670 2:1'>1 Pt 2:1</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to a specific locality for placement <b><i>put away, put</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><a href='B:470 14:3'>Mt 14:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀποτελέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀποτινάσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}